{"tid":903862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「雙11」新盤劈價30萬人仔　業主喊不公求退貨","createTime":"2018-11-16T01:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T05:05:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1a7a43bafecf43b07aa5a6b66d10b125236162","tid":903862,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181116/photo/bkn-20181116033818368-1116_00952_001_01p.jpg?20181116085516\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181116%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181116033818368-1116_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20181116085516&h=adfedb93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n江蘇無錫10多名新業主上周六（10日）帶備寫有「還我血汗錢」的橫額，到當地一個新樓盤的售樓處示威，抗議售樓商一個月內減價30萬元（人民幣．下同，約34萬港元），並要求退房。樓盤營業部負責人回應稱，這是一個「雙11」期間，為再購單位等的業主提供的優惠，不存在減價行為。 <br />\n<br />\n涉事苦主為已購買中海寰宇天下物業的新業主，有業主稱，他於10月時以每平方米14800元（約16971港元）入市，不過其同事後來則以每平方米13000元（約14907港元）購得單位，一個月足足每平方米大減2000元（約2293港元），以整體樓價計，差額近達30萬元。 <br />\n<br />\n業主稱，「房價一下子降這麼多，我們業主心裡怎麼接受的了，畢竟誰的錢都不是大風刮來的呀，我們的訴求就是退房」，同時已向地產銷售員等反映事件，惟對方及發展商均否認有降價行為。後來有售樓處員工表示，現時高層單位仍處於每平方米14700元（約16856港元）水平，之前的「降價」實為「雙11」活動。 <br />\n<br />\n售樓處員工補充指，今次活動對象為已購買旗下品牌物業的業主，若再購另一單位或推薦直屬親友購買則可獲優惠，而活動則於上周四（8日）至周四（15日）舉行。無錫房地產協會副會長兼秘書長沈詢表示，房價只要符合物價局、住建局的要求，促銷是沒有問題。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181116/photo/bkn-20181116033818368-1116_00952_001_02p.jpg?20181116085516\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181116%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181116033818368-1116_00952_001_02p.jpg%3F20181116085516&h=f5e072bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181116/photo/bkn-20181116033818368-1116_00952_001_03p.jpg?20181116085516\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181116%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181116033818368-1116_00952_001_03p.jpg%3F20181116085516&h=74c5179c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181116/bkn-20181116033818368-1116_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181116%2Fbkn-20181116033818368-1116_00952_001.html&d=MpvUtDhoU6d9xR18VsuFQzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c752c325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181116/bkn-20181116033818368-1116_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f3958e30fd94d06e54ad8b2a6de3601ca1a4245a","tid":903862,"uid":71215,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:56:22.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要 核突支那Style<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2356bdea58ec7026207e84c3530a5fb2e79454","tid":903862,"uid":522,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T01:56:52.000Z","msg":"同香港人一樣 只許升不準跌"},{"pid":"9053b644efac5d5c2839e3c165c077dc2f828c1f","tid":903862,"uid":39527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:08:25.000Z","msg":"如果調轉1個月升30萬會點  輸打贏要垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"092f470068135cb9e25c79d8cd2416d74832fe7f","tid":903862,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:09:58.000Z","msg":"支國人真係好撚無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一堆連登支那狗再吹捧  都改唔到劣等呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d86f2b6841dfb4ddd2d15a80f56f508f9d73822","tid":903862,"uid":3775,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T02:43:34.000Z","msg":"如果香港係咁會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d74fe39845dc210e7c3de2e5a966f3f6ca27b3","tid":903862,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2